-- MOVES-Barclays energy analyst James West to join ISI Group
-- 
-- Thu Jul 17, 2014 07:40PM EDT
-- None



July 17 (Reuters) - Research and brokerage firm International Strategy & Investment Group LLC (ISI Group) has hired Barclays Plc's <BARC.L> leading oil services and drilling analyst James West, the Wall Street Journal reported.

West, who will join ISI in September, has already left Barclays, according to the report. (http://on.wsj.com/UdPF4o)ISI Group President Vinayak Singh confirmed the appointment to the Journal. Barclays was not immediately available for comment.